                                                        <br />
                                                        <li><b>K & C Machine: </b>K&C TEST RIG : Kinematics and Compliance Rig are several components. This Single Axle Suspension Kinematics and Compliance Deflection Test System shall include the following major subsystems which are as follows:</li>
                                                        <ol>
                                                            <li>Platform modules</li>
                                                            <li>Load reaction frame and body clamp system</li>
                                                            <li>Position and Load Transducers</li>
                                                            <li>Controls and instrumentation system</li>
                                                            <li>Data analysis system</li>
                                                            <li>Steering wheel robot</li>
                                                            <li>Hydraulic System or power transformer.</li>
                                                        </ol>
                                                        <li><b>Steering Test Rig: </b>This test rig is capable of  durability testing of all kind of automotive steering systems.</li>
